[Student "S"]
{This is the companion to Deal 22.

Again, worried about a possible trump loser in addition to the missing Ace, NORTH 
bids 5\D, the Queen Ask.

SOUTH definitely does NOT have the \HQ. But with five trumps she 
does know that NORTH probably does not have a trump loser so she jumps 
to 6\H anyway.}

